pipeline_summary.name: Daily Sales Report
pipeline_summary.description: Generates daily sales reports by querying PostgreSQL, converting the result to CSV, creating a PDF chart, and emailing the final report to management.

components.name: Query Sales Data
components.description: Extracts daily aggregated sales data from the PostgreSQL database using the execution date as a filter.

components.name: Transform Sales Data to CSV
components.description: Converts the extracted sales aggregation into a CSV file using pandas.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful extraction of sales data.

components.name: Generate PDF Chart
components.description: Creates a PDF barchart visualization of the sales data using matplotlib.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after CSV report has been generated.

connections.purpose: Read CSV and write PDF chart

components.name: Email Sales Report
components.description: Emails the CSV report and PDF chart to the management team with a datespecific subject line.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after both CSV and PDF files have been created.

description.default: Generates daily sales reports by querying PostgreSQL, converting the result to CSV, creating a PDF chart, and emailing the final report to management.

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

postgres_conn_id.description: Connection ID for the PostgreSQL database

provide_context.description: Flag to provide Airflow context to the Python callable
Flag to provide Airflow context to the Python callable

to.description: Recipient email address for the sales report

files.description: List of file paths to attach to the email

sources: PostgreSQL sales table (daily aggregated sales data)
sinks: Email delivery to management (management@company.com) with CSV and PDF attachments
